<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM2.6.8">
<l>miṉṉiṭaic cītai poruṭṭā vilaṅkaiyar</l>
<l>maṉṉaṉ maṇimuṭi pattu muṭaṉvīḻa</l>
<l>taṉṉika roṉṟillāc cilaikāl vaḷaittiṭṭa</l>
<l>miṉṉu muṭiyaṟkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā</l>
<l rend="indent">vēlai yaṭaittāṟkōr kōlkoṇṭuvā.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Bring a staff for the one with the lightning crown</l>
<l rend="indent">who bent the shaft of the bow that is without an equal so that</l>
<l rend="indent">the ten jewelled crowns of the king of Laṅkā fell all at once</l>
<l rend="indent">for the sake of Sītā with the lightning[-thin] waist.</l>
<l>Bring a staff for the one who damned the sea.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
